text: Gaelle De Rycke (born 20 October 1981) is a French water polo player. She was a member of the France women's national water polo team at the 2003 World Aquatics Championships. On a club level, she played for Union Saint-Bruno. == References == == Other websites == * liste-officielle-sportifs-de-haut- niveau/informations-sportif *liste-officielle-sportifs-de-haut-niveau Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:French water polo players
